Depends: R (>= 3.0.0), sf, sp, qpdf
Suggests: geoR, dplyr, PrevMap, rmarkdown, testthat, viridisLite,raster, knitr
Description: This package utilises the functoinality provided by the OSMData and 
    geosample to allow users to create spatially continuous or discrete
    random samples from a pre-defined spatial border using OSM data. 
